<h1 class="mt-5">Welcome to this online test for {{title}}</h1>



<p>This is an online-based perception test and is completely voluntary and can be stopped at any time. </p>
<p>The first part contains some background questions, then the main part starts.

% if training:
Before the actual test starts you will go through a short training phase to get used to the task.
% end
You will see short videos and are asked to watch and explore them by pressing your left mouse key and moving the mouse.
Further details on the instructions are shown after the background questions.

</p>


<p>
The test will take approximately 10-15 minutes. In case you need a short break in-between, you can stop at any time but only when you keep the browser open.
At the end of the test you can have the chance to win one out of three 10â‚¬ vouchers (Amazon or PayPal).
To participate in this small raffle, please take care to write down your email address into the feedback form after you have watched all videos.
</p>
<p>
You need a screen of at least 1920x1080 resolution and a quiet environment without any distractions.
As browser please use Chrome, Microsoft Edge or Firefox. Safari will not work.
</p>

<p>
We collect the answers to the questions and mouse movements for every stimuli.
In addition, we collect data about the used browser (browser agent) and the size of the used browser window for analysis purposes.
All data is stored in <strong>anonymized</strong> form and will be treated confidentially.
For management purposes this page uses <strong>cookies</strong>.
</p>

